title: O'Neill Girls - Freeride camp
description:
It's the third time that O'Neill has presented the Girl's Freeride Coaching session in Oberstdorf. The three day camps focus on how to approach and have fun in the back country.
The girls get supported by our team riders Bibi Pekarek and Lisa Veith with the Hindelanger Bergführerbüro in charge of the tours and safety of all participants.
It's the first time the O'Neill Girls Freeride Coaching has included a skiing group and it was a great success for the girls and O'Neill.
